              <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Graduate Scholarship — FAPERJ Nota 10 (Fundação de Amparo à Pesquisa do Estado do Rio de Janeiro).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 shrink-0 sm:w-28">2025–2026</span>
              <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Graduate Scholarship — CAPES (Coordenação de Aperfeiçoamento de Pessoal de Nível Superior).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 shrink-0 sm:w-28">2021–2022</span>
