              <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Institutional Scientific Initiation Scholarship — FGV.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 shrink-0 sm:w-28">2019–2024</span>
              <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">90% Merit Scholarship for undergraduate studies at FGV, awarded for outstanding performance in the entrance examination.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="subsection-title">Distinctions</h3>
          <div class="divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800">
