              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 shrink-0 sm:w-28">2025</span>
              <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Professor Carlos Eduardo Sarmento Academic Distinction Award, School of Social Sciences (FGV CPDOC), for achieving the highest academic performance among the Class of 2025 undergraduate students.</p>
